<emphasis box="[937,1037,660,684]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="236">T. hatakei</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Ochi, T. &amp; Kawahara, M. &amp; Inagaki, M." pageId="13" pageNumber="236" pagination="25 - 34" refId="ref8681" refString="Ochi, T., Kawahara, M. &amp; Inagaki, M. (2019) Four new Psammodiini species from Japan (Coleoptera, Scarabaeidae). Kogane, 22, 25 - 34." type="journal article" year="2019">Ochi, Kawahara &amp; Inagaki, 2019</bibRefCitation>
